STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Shane Michael JACOBS, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0160 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

The defendant appeals from his sentences for willful injury causing bodily injury and domestic abuse assault by impeding airflow. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
